         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><salute><pb facs="1892_AS_RBH_2_00026"/>Lieber Richard,</salute></opener><p>mein <rs ref="#pmb12695" type="person">Papa</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>agt mir zu, auch für Sie den <rs ref="#pmb31971" type="work">Musotte</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Sitz zu be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>orgen.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t<lb/> Ihr <signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div>
